gomodel:SYNGO_2390  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: ARFGAP1 was detected by immunoblot analyses to be present in LP1 (synaptosomal membranes) in subcellular fractions of the brain.. Experimental description: Materials and Methods \"Full-length human ArfGAP1, Arf1 was cloned into the mammalian expression vector cDNA3.1/nV5-DEST and Escherichia coli expression vector pDEST15 with a GST tag (Invitrogen) from an entry clone carrying ArfGAP1 full-lengthcDNA(Invitrogen Ultimate ORF Clone IOH57771) or Arf1 (Invitrogen Ultimate ORF Clone IOH13571) byGateway technology." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5615-1014" ;
